<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shivalik Hostel Mess</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic Styling */
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #003366; /* Deep Blue */
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: #003366; /* Deep Blue */
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
            font-weight: semi-bold;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .guidelines {
            background-color: #F5F9FC; /* Very Light Blue */
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        table, th, td {
            border: 1px solid #003366; /* Deep Blue */
        }

        th, td {
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #FF6F61; /* Coral */
            color: #FFFFFF; /* White */
        }

        td {
            background-color: #FFE5B4; /* Lighter Coral */
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #003366; /* Deep Blue */
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 2px solid #003366;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }

        .small-font {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #777;
        }

        hr {
            margin: 30px 0;
            border: 1px solid #003366; /* Deep Blue */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Shivalik Hostel Mess</h1>

        <!-- General Guidelines Section -->
        <div class="guidelines">
            <h2>General Guidelines</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Mess SOP for Self-kitchen. Please follow the guidelines and maintain cleanliness in the kitchen area.</li>
                <li>Extra messing is available in lunch (till 1:30 PM) every day* except Wednesday, Saturday, and Sunday.</li>
                <li>Maintaining cleanliness in the mess area is everyone's responsibility. Dispose of waste properly and avoid littering.</li>
                <li>For any special dietary requirements or preferences, kindly inform the mess office in advance. We strive to accommodate all reasonable requests.</li>
                <li>To avail of extra-messing benefits, please collect the necessary coupons from the mess office.</li>
                <li>Please adhere to the mess timings strictly. Latecomers may not be served, so plan your meals accordingly. Dinner after 9:05 PM is strictly for sportspeople only.</li>
                <li>If you encounter any issues with your meal, such as finding it unsatisfactory or discovering foreign objects in the food, please notify the mess staff or the manager immediately.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Meal Plan Table -->
        <h2>Weekly Meal Plan</h2>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Breakfast</th>
                <th>Lunch</th>
                <th>Evening Snacks</th>
                <th>Dinner</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Poori Bhaji</td>
                <td>Dal Rice</td>
                <td>Tea & Biscuits</td>
                <td>Paneer Curry</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Idli Sambhar</td>
                <td>Rajma Rice</td>
                <td>Pakoras</td>
                <td>Chicken Curry</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Aloo Paratha</td>
                <td>Mixed Veg Curry</td>
                <td>Fruit Salad</td>
                <td>Egg Curry</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Uttapam</td>
                <td>Chole Rice</td>
                <td>Samosa</td>
                <td>Dal Tadka</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Bread Butter</td>
                <td>Dal Fry</td>
                <td>Tea & Chips</td>
                <td>Fish Fry</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Pav Bhaji</td>
                <td>Veg Biryani</td>
                <td>Milk & Cookies</td>
                <td>Paneer Butter Masala</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Dosa Sambhar</td>
                <td>Chicken Biryani</td>
                <td>Cold Coffee</td>
                <td>Special Thali</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Sanket Patil - Mess Secretary, Shivalik Hostel, IIT Delhi</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
